Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.71,0:00:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.17,0:00:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let go of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.84,0:00:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.17,0:00:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.79,0:01:44.91,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(212,200)\pos(325,343)}Welcome Home
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.15,0:01:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Male.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.57,0:01:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,German-Czechoslovakian.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.87,0:02:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After World War II, as the eldest son in\Nhis family, he remained in Bohemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A soldier who graduated from a military academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An elite who was the nation's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,names don't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Female.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.98,0:02:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only daughter born to an elementary\Nschool teacher in Moravia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.82,0:02:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blonde hair, blue eyes... a beautiful girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She attended Brno University, majoring in genetics.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.04,0:02:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A talented woman in whom her\Nprofessors saw a great future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,names don't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:03:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two met at a caf{\fnMeiryo U}é{\fnNarkisim} in Prague.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.60,0:03:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't take them long to fall in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She soon became pregnant...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he confessed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that this was all a mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Race, brains, bone structure, athletic ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to create children between\Nthe best and brightest...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,experiments were conducted\Ninvolving dozens of couples.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He explained that he carried out his mission\Naccording to the scenario, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he no longer intended to see it through, and said...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The couple ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he said that he wasn't\Ngoing to stick to the scenario...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that very action was already taken into account.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The woman was placed in an isolated room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's on a new assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's on a new assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's on a new assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The woman said...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let me see him."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let me see him."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let me see him."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let me see him."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The woman knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that he was probably no longer of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The babies within her were growing steadily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Face this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had started to realize that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.78,0:06:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this man who often came by...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this man who sketched her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this man was the mastermind behind the experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.47,0:06:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I die, these babies, growing \N inside me, will definitely have their revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say curious things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her nine months passed, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the time to give birth had come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To prepare for the delivery...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:06:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she was moved to another room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.67,0:07:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, she made her move.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A space only a few centimeters wide...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy with child and shaking with terrible contractions...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she escaped through the ventilation system.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She collapsed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on the street, several meters from the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her water had already broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How beautiful they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:08:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the babies who will lead\Nof humanity's future, aren't they
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came up with their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.87,0:08:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to think of such unnecessary things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came up with...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their names...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I want to name them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Name them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for names.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan asked me where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bonaparta's still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I won't forgive. I will never forgive you."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Even if I die these babies, growing \Ninside me, will definitely get their revenge."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franz Bonaparta's still alive isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.21,0:09:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some doctor you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a hospital up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you tell me where Johan is, I'll take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, you'll bleed to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.76,0:10:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shot me, made me bleed this much,\Nand now you're threatening me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a pay phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call the hospital and tell them someone's\Nbleeding to death in a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy might tell us where Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His life will be in danger if we keep him here any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you can't change who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't kill someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.79,0:12:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where Johan is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenzou, an ambulance is on its way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.81,0:12:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, let's run away from...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Kenzou?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left a message for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I can't get you involved in this any further."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I ruined your life."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm really sorry... Please be happy."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire coming from the Three Frogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, eat as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you eat that fast, you'll choke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must have been starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.24,0:16:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't talk at all, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've eaten, we'll hear your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:17:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those kids may not have any parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they have parents, they might have\Nreasons for not wanting to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We wanted children, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.36,0:17:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could take care of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such stupid things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, that was harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go give these to the man and the lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I have a good plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I said wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:19:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I ran away from the Red Rose Mansion,\Nwent home to the Three Frogs...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you welcomed me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this timer I'll say it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heidelberg...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our twentieth birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I went to get you, a lot of time has passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to get me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.74,0:19:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Fortner... Mr. Liebert...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the people who have been kind to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You killed everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.97,0:19:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.31,0:19:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:20:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said that it's nice out today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Driver...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you go a little faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:29.06,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you shoot me like you did before?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll end everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:20:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,End?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is "the end"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,End...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,End...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,End...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,End...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.35,0:21:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,End...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,End.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen "the end of the world," time and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is "the end"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die, and I'll die, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.54,0:21:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've seen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.17,0:21:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.46,0:21:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.27,0:22:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.37,0:22:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the actual, horrible story.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.38,0:22:26.51,Default Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.91,0:22:31.08,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,471)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:44.51,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,475)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:44.51,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(201,21)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:47.47,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:23:01.15,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(198,472)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:23:01.15,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,21)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:26.01,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,473)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.01,0:23:34.43,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,473)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:36.89,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,472)}Make it home
